Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,影　Shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.25,0:02:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第四章　流転
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鴉逗女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.73,0:05:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從那時候開始染上血的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳的身體確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.49,0:05:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳的力量，全部交給我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,凡是妨礙我的人　必須全部解決掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鴉逗女，妳在這裡幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還不回屋子裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.43,0:07:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鴉逗女，妳聽不到我說什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只會　按我自己的意志行事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.28,0:07:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已經　不會再聽儀助的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:07:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鴉逗女．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鴉逗女就託付給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請問　有什麼事情找我．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那裡不是說話的地方　進來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是　是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我有事要問你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是　請問
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,姓陳的被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請問那有．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我沒有下過命令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請　請看這個．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是跟平常一樣　按照上面寫的去求葵幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.65,0:09:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是　在上次那個隱藏的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你還不明白？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果姓陳的現在死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鴉片的滾滾財源就會化為烏有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你打算怎麼處理？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還不住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,華龍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.08,0:11:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,孫六
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳最好乖乖別動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:24.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我有件事要告訴妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,中計了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:11:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:12:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是假的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全靠它　妳才捲進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其實葵交給妳的任務　差不多都是．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不對　是全部都是．．．\N說了也不要緊　都是某人的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,某人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和被妳幹掉的外國人在一起的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底　是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,暗之十藏　一個恐怖的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為了目的不擇手段
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要是妨礙他的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算是同伴也無所顧忌　一定要處決掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是　一個連神都畏懼的殺人集團的首領
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他身邊的殺手　幾乎沒有一個是沒換過的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說起來　華龍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳應該很清楚他才對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.21,0:13:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很久以前　妳還是小孩子的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被人從家裡擄走　全家人被殺害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.89,0:13:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是那個男的　有錯嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,孫六
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是把我聽到的東西告訴妳而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過仔細想想　這事對妳打擊真大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然被自己的仇人養大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個男人　現在在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:57.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那之前　我還是告訴妳一些有趣的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:13:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有一個秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,秘密？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不對　妳還是不要知道比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,孫六
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉　我要先溜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他的總部　就在那條外國人的船裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然對誰都沒出手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然只是短時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遇上妳真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們會再見的　等妳武藝高強了再來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:47.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你等等　孫六
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.15,0:15:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,逆賊華龍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳聽著　我不會讓妳逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算追到天邊　也要把妳碎屍萬段
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.57,0:15:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,身手不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不愧是自小培育出來的一流忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我果然應該早就殺了妳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳想報仇嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我還不至於被妳的氣勢嚇倒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不愧是做忍者的人才
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳想起妳父親的劍技了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.29,0:17:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,華龍，妳很想知道妳們家為什麼會遇襲吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哼！因為妳的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看到了不該看的東西　而且還妨礙我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對我們來說　他是最大的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就為此殺了他？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳為什麼用那種目光看我？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳應該知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在這泰平之世　隨時都與死亡相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以這規則開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所有這一切都是為了生存
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.19,0:18:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我再告訴妳點有趣的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳父親見到的　並不是只有我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.71,0:18:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當時葵也在場
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.23,0:19:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在死之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葵要親手除去他的後人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才把妳培育成忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳成長在自己仇人的手上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.75,0:19:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底　怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,特別是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要選像妳那樣　將來有希望的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是那個男人．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.14,0:20:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不會手下留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,馬上送你下地獄！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.44,0:21:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳無路可退了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.86,0:21:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼要對我如此憎恨？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.36,0:21:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,華龍啊　你不記得她了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個時候就是一時仁慈　放了她一條生路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.83,0:22:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.42,0:22:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我之所以變成今天這樣　全是妳的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.93,0:22:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.95,0:22:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,血？血？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,0:22:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼妳．．．會和那個男人．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.21,0:23:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他把全部告訴我了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.63,0:23:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳就是那個時候的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.05,0:23:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以才把妳引到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.55,0:23:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳把孫六．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.56,0:23:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒錯　今天就在這裡來個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.91,0:23:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,血？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.75,0:23:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,血？血？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.42,0:23:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的血還可以這樣．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.26,0:23:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,華龍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.77,0:24:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快點　華龍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.13,0:24:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鴉逗女！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.63,0:24:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,儀助．．．這樣就．．．一切．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.14,0:24:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一切．．．都結束了．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.88,0:25:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鴉逗女的父親和我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.71,0:25:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以前就是同一族的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.97,0:25:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鴉逗女的父親覺悟到泰平之世
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.47,0:25:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,捨棄忍者之道
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.97,0:26:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,脫離族人　選擇了庶民之路
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.23,0:26:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是那個男人　暗之十藏
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.06,0:26:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,決不饒恕他這個決定
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.82,0:26:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個男人不知從什麼時候開始
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.65,0:26:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就統領著一族的忍者　並把他們當作殺手來利用
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.50,0:26:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她父親囑託過我　千萬不能讓鴉逗女踏上忍者之路
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.17,0:26:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.01,0:26:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鴉逗女始終還是　不得不以我的雙手來解決
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.77,0:26:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鴉逗女從小　一見到血
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.85,0:26:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就變得誰也不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.11,0:26:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她無論踏上哪條路　結果可能都只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.87,0:27:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.45,0:27:05.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都是我．．．都是我．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.29,0:27:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果不是我　對鴉逗女的父親出手的話．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.96,0:27:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鴉逗女她　最後還是和我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.63,0:27:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我　讓她走上了和我一樣的命運之路
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.48,0:27:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原諒我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.49,0:27:43.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳以後怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.92,0:27:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.84,0:28:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,華龍　從今以後天下會有大變
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.43,0:28:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,甚至　武士的時代可能會結束
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.69,0:28:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.45,0:28:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,菊花
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.29,0:28:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們太過分了　兩個人自己走了不等我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.62,0:28:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.46,0:28:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這不是明擺著的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.13,0:28:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葵屋裡面沒了華龍小姐　無聊死了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.30,0:28:42.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我決定了要和你們一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.39,0:28:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒問題　我跟那邊的人說了要出來旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.72,0:28:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放心好了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.06,0:28:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們．．．一起．．．
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.89,0:28:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒錯　和妳一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.57,0:28:59.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂　你幹什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.99,0:29:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這只死松鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.40,0:29:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,停下來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.75,0:29:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊　等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.76,0:29:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我追不上你們啦